Patch Set 1:

This is more of question. Is there a case anytime where image is in saving state with location? like in copy_from ?

Patch Set 1:

Iccha:

By convention, there is not. We want to avoid repeating the mistake we made with Images; namely, entities really shouldn't exist until they are usable. The "pending_delete" status is just there to help us on the backend track which locations need to be deleted and when. It will not be exposed to customers.
